# MomentumCVG workflow

- Read `docs/agenda/current_sprint.md` at session start.
- Default: inspect and plan before editing code.
- Respect sprint **mode**: Audit (no edits), Verification (tests only), Build (approved scope only).
- v1 spec lives in `docs/v1_spec_pins.md`; do not expand scope without user approval.
- `docs/archive/` is stale reference — do not update archived files.
- After edits: run relevant pytest subset and report results.
- Use venv: `C:/MomentumCVG_env/venv/Scripts/python.exe`
